Installation Instructions
*************************

Basic Installation
==================

   Briefly, the shell command `./configure && make && sudo make install'
should configure, build, and install this package. `sudo make uninstall` to 
remove this package.See README for further details. 


Compilers and Options
=====================

     ./configure --enable-debug to compile with DEBUG set, which prints lots
of messages to stdout.

   *Note Defining Variables::, for more details.


Installation Names
==================

   By default, `make install' installs the package's modules under
`/usr/lib', which consists of /usr/lib/libnss_rightscale.so.2.0.x
